divs: Sighting DetailsIt was just about midnight and I was taking the pooches for a stroll when i saw a huge bright light dart about 40 degrees in a westward direction and remain there. Continued the stroll checking periodically and it remained. Put poochies to bed came back out with coffee and it was still there sort of pulsing and changing from really bright to slightly duller and back again. It appeared to be moving in a small erratic pattern while at its brightest. This continued for almost 2 hours it never moved. Went in to refill coffee and pooooof it was gone no trace in sight. My daughter also witnessed this event. The photos with "a" at the end have been enlarged the others are the originals.
